WEBVTT

00:05:59.438 --> 00:06:01.192
in traditional medicine

00:06:01.192 --> 00:06:03.872
against respiratory problems.

00:06:03.872 --> 00:06:05.961
Now, our preliminary labwork

00:06:05.961 --> 00:06:07.693
on the leaf extract has shown

00:06:07.693 --> 00:06:11.822
that precisely these 
leaves contain ingredients

00:06:11.822 --> 00:06:14.917
that are very close, 
in terms of structures,

00:06:14.917 --> 00:06:17.283
chemical structures, to those medicines

00:06:17.283 --> 00:06:18.802
which are sold in the chemist's shop

00:06:18.802 --> 00:06:20.777
against asthma.

00:06:20.777 --> 00:06:22.687
So who knows

00:06:22.687 --> 00:06:24.773
what humanity will benefit from

00:06:24.773 --> 00:06:30.191
should this plant decide 
to reveal all its secrets.